{"type": "article", "id": 22782, "title": "Jordan 迷们，去香港不要错过这间亚洲最大旗舰店", "description": "最丰富的展示和最全方位的体验", "date": "2016-02-24T17:46:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6461, "name": "乔丹"}, {"id": 193, "name": "香港"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 2084, "name": "亚洲"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 5487, "name": "Jordan"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 230, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702160846OiLZsIcSJ50KnvDh.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Jordan Brand 继十月于美国芝加哥开幕 32 South State 旗舰店后，采用新概念的亚洲最大旗舰店 Jordan 8 Wellington 最近落户香港中环威灵顿街。值得一逛，球鞋迷、乔丹粉丝们别错过。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021608367IJvfHO1AnlVi9cq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160836EGXgMBlJNnFdywkQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160837KXvqabfI8dxTkRWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">店铺外部挂着 Michael Jordan 巨幅海报的玻璃幕墙格外引人注目。店内 4000 平方英尺（约 371 平方米）的面积，装修风格和细节处处也都是在向这位 NBA 传奇球星致敬，讲述他的职业生涯以及对于 Jordan 品牌发展至今历程的回顾。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160838VzHLMefXEBIGD7w6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160839ynVOJkT7zR9uBdfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49576271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160840DH9uQt27JwmoIMOs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65434381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">有一面墙上陈列着 29 双 Air Jordan I-XXX 全系列金色版本，可以说是 Air Jordan 的一个小型展览。香港当地的艺术家 Michael Lau 则用小的金色乔丹雕像创作出 Jumpman 的立体 logo。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160840yvmSPC3foDVOzpB0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160841OhHyxvsf5WJYKzb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160842guefQwSVl1Ldh95n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">新概念则不只体现在店面的视觉效果上，更多是在于购物体验和服务。 Jordan.com  的会员可享受球鞋保养、个性定制服务。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160843wTbcRgp5msDztJFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160843DJaYkXTE9wePgSiN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160845fWOeL7NnyR1UtDIC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">球鞋试穿的区域还可以根据屏幕上播放视频的示范动作来更全面感受各款球鞋，以找到运动状态下最合适的鞋款。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160845k7XYFV4x3I0BreT9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">部分图片来自：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/2/hong-kong-jordan-8-wellington-grand-opening\">Hypebeast</a></p>\n\n"}